f=Brand Studio/muse/custom/concept-library/SKILL.md · in=concept-library muse's memory: per-brand registry campaign concepts **used, rejected, reserved** new ideation run dedupes against before anything goes forward. Generation without memory produces "fresh" idea six months; skill makes muse's creativity cumulative way weave's ledger makes story cumulative. · p=Three failure modes, one registry. *Repeats*: pitching concept brand already ran (or already rejected, rejection reason forgotten). *Lost work*: strong concepts lost bake-off vanishing instead reserved right moment. *Unlearned rejections*: spark's operator's "no" carrying reasoning never gets consulted again. registry captures three, ideation run starts what brand already knows. · wu=Triggers: "campaign ideas," "new concept," "have done before," "what's reserve" automatically closing phase `generate-creative-ideas` run campaign/content concepts. · st:/ Protocol=`Ideation run produces candidates (via generate-creative-ideas — typically 10 per brief) \· -> DEDUPE each vs the registry: match on mechanism + angle, not just wording \· new / variant-of-[entry] / repeat-of-[entry] \· -> Variants: name what's genuinely new vs the prior entry \· -> Survivors scored (NAF, from the sibling skill) → top 3 to spark for coherence` · h3:Phase 1 — Dedupe=Match candidates against registry **mechanism angle**, surface wording "customers tell their worst-old-way story" concept whether it's framed contest series. Verdicts candidate: **new**, **variant** (name delta whether clears prior entry's rejection reason), **repeat** (cite entry; repeats *used* concepts return deliberate callbacks weave's ledger, never amnesia). · h3:Phase Score Forward=Survivors get NAF scores (the sibling skill's default rubric flagged rule 0.6 judgment rubric, validated instrument). Top spark coherence sanity check (coach mode) before any development spend; spark's read comes back develop park kill-with-reason. · h3:Phase Register Everything=candidate reached scoring gets registry entry status: · h3:Phase Register Everything=**used** went development; updated later what happened (kai's numbers available) registry's learning loop., **rejected** *actual* reason (off-arc, off-voice, spark kill, operator pass, lost bake-off). "Didn't feel right" reason; ask real one., **reserved** good concept, wrong moment; trigger it's waiting (season, product launch, arc act II). Reserves reviewed cadence shelf doesn't become graveyard. · h3:Phase Register Everything=Registry append-only; status changes new lines referencing entry (the system's ledger discipline). · of=`## Concept Run: [brief, one line] — [brand] \·  \· \| # \| Concept (mechanism + angle) \| Dedupe \| NAF \| Forward? \| \· \|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\| \· ` · pr=**Mechanism-level dedupe.** Rewording old concept isn't new concept., **Rejections carry reasons.** "no" without teaches nothing re-pitched., **Reserved status, euphemism.** reserve names trigger gets cadence review., **Outcomes close loop.** Used concepts get their results attached registry learning set, filing cabinet., **Append-only.** discipline ledger system., **NAF rubric.** Flagged rule 0.6 until muse's logical layer gets real creativity-evaluation source. · f=Empty registry (new brand) concept "new"; registry starts run., Brief novel nothing match say so; dedupe cost near-zero, skipping amnesia starts., Prior campaigns exist unregistered backfill published work labeled reconstructions (weave's ledger pattern). · b:with Other Skills=`generate-creative-ideas` (sibling) produces candidates scoring rubrics; skill owns memory, dedupe, forward/register protocol., **spark** sanity-checks top (coach) later gates developed creative (gate) two different moments., **weave** positions developed concepts chapters; repeat-as-callback weave's call, muse's., **kai** supplies outcome data used entries. **pulse/lena/pixel** develop what survives.